96
00:10:26,630 --> 00:10:29,250
You really care about your Boss Ning.

97
00:10:29,710 --> 00:10:30,750
Unfortunately,

98
00:10:30,990 --> 00:10:32,390
your Boss Ning

99
00:10:32,750 --> 00:10:36,080
