100
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:38,550
Old Chief.

101
00:10:39,410 --> 00:10:40,180
Zhao Ji.

102
00:10:45,750 --> 00:10:46,780
Ning Yuanzhou,

103
00:10:48,370 --> 00:10:49,930
